added some tests for PieceTree. Need to go back to Tree tests and add some for IndexedNode handling.

Modified add and search to allow for indexedNodes
New code implemented using GetChildrenIndexes means that list type nodes and Index type nodes can be searched using the same interfaces. Also added FindChildByIndex, allowing the system to search by an index without knowing the class type

tests and production code for backup method/modifications to AddNote
added unit tests and code that puts notes in place when backing up/forwarding. May need adjustments made to direction and expression additions

Modifications to AttachDirection and AttachExpression methods
Modified Direction and Expression so that new additions: - check their pathway is clear (aka no child in that slot): if it is, add to the current note node - if the pathway isn't clear: check the slot has a value. If it doesn't, replace Nothing with the new node's value - if the pathway isn't clear and the slot does have a value: keep looking for the next slot, starting with that child.
